t month of the year. January has the lowest average temperature of the year. It is 25.5&nbsp;\u00b0C. Between the driest and wettest months, the difference in precipitation is 440&nbsp;mm. During the year, the average temperatures vary by 3.7&nbsp;\u00b0C.\n\n{{Weather box\n|location = Mandaluyong\n|metric first = Yes\n|single line = Yes\n|Jan high C = 29.7\n|Feb high C = 30.5\n|Mar high C = 32.1\n|Apr high C = 33.7\n|May high C = 33.8\n|Jun high C = 32.3\n|Jul high C = 31.1\n|Aug high C = 30.6\n|Sep high C = 30.7\n|Oct high C = 30.9\n|Nov high C = 30.4\n|Dec high C = 29.7\n|year high C = \n|Jan mean C = 25.5\n|Feb mean C = 25.9\n|Mar mean C = 27.2\n|Apr mean C = 28.7\n|May mean C = 29.2\n|Jun mean C = 28.4\n|Jul mean C = 27.6\n|Aug mean C = 27.3\n|Sep mean C = 27.2\n|Oct mean C = 27.2\n|Nov mean C = 26.7\n|Dec mean C = 25.9\n|year mean C = \n|Jan low C = 21.3\n|Feb low C = 21.4\n|Mar low C = 22.4\n|Apr low C = 23.8\n|May low C = 24.7\n|Jun low C = 24.5\n|Jul low C = 24.1\n|Aug low C = 24.0\n|Sep low C = 23.8\n|Oct low C = 23.5\n|Nov low C = 23.0\n|Dec low C = 22.1\n|year low C = \n|Jan precipitation mm = 13.5\n|Feb precipitation mm = 7.3\n|Mar precipitation mm = 21.4\n|Apr precipitation mm = 18.7\n|May precipitation mm = 138.6\n|Jun precipitation mm = 283.8\n|Jul precipitation mm = 364.1\n|Aug precipitation mm = 476.3\n|Sep precipitation mm = 334.1\n|Oct precipitation mm = 200.5\n|Nov precipitation mm = 111.4\n|Dec precipitation mm = 56.0\n|year precipitation mm = \n|Jan rain days = 4\n|Feb rain days = 2\n|Mar rain days = 3\n|Apr rain days = 3\n|May rain days = 10\n|Jun rain days = 16\n|Jul rain days = 22\n|Aug rain days = 22\n|Sep rain days = 20\n|Oct rain days = 18\n|Nov rain days = 14\n|Dec rain days = 9\n|unit rain days = 0.10 mm\n|Jan humidity = 72\n|Feb humidity = 73\n|Mar humidity = 66\n|Apr humidity = 64\n|May humidity = 68\n|Jun humidity = 76\n|Jul humidity = 80\n|Aug humidity = 83\n|Sep humidity = 81\n|Oct humidity = 78\n|Nov humidity = 76\n|Dec humidity 